ðŸ’¡ Tip
You can chain Gfetchert directly with any ML or GIS pipeline:


rain = get_rainfall(lat=27.1, lon=88.6, start="2023-08-01", end="2023-08-31")
rain.to_csv("sikkim_august_rainfall.csv", index=False)




